{"type":"article_comment","id":11635,"parentType":"article","parentId":2024,"uid":6513,"contents":"薄熙来和他的好兄弟（“新四人帮”）<br>\n<br>\n1.同框最多的好兄弟·<b>徐才厚</b><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7WWZZtl.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7WWZZtl.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7WWZZtl.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n曾经紧紧握手的好兄弟如今已是阴阳两隔。<br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwU31sd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwU31sd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwU31sd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3okiOae.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3okiOae.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3okiOae.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n共看阅兵。<br>\n（王沪宁也同框了，而且有不可靠消息称王沪宁要为薄熙来翻案？）<br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnMrEXQ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnMrEXQ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnMrEXQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JPT3Jhd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JPT3Jhd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JPT3Jhd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NqonXWv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NqonXWv.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NqonXWv.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n2.据说公开挺薄的好兄弟·<b>周永康</b>（有传闻周薄要联手政变？）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/G6xXgRo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G6xXgRo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/G6xXgRo.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n以下三张图来自YouTube某节目<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AdTVTOs.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AdTVTOs.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AdTVTOs.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ESD09ws.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ESD09ws.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ESD09ws.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/icAsTHs.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/icAsTHs.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/icAsTHs.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n3.“新四人帮”另一位成员令计划，和薄的交集没有多少资料。两个人的共同点就是被姓谷的老婆拉下水，被开法拉利的孩子拉下水。（然而据薄瓜瓜的自证发声，他那天乘坐的是司机的黑色奥迪，并未开一辆红色法拉利。）","date":"2020-05-12","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}